{"tid":1632061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想畀意見嘅 可唔可以檢討下你啲用字？","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:54:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T17:45:54.000Z","uid":219901,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c1f67ed2140177b10528de3d7ad060906837f990","tid":1632061,"uid":219901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:54:47.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n今日出現大量呢兩種post：<br />\n<strong>1. 勇武過晒火，裝修要有原則，唔可以殺紅了眼（下刪三萬字）<br />\n2. 抱怨連登容唔下第二種意見，同林鄭無分別乜乜柒柒</strong><br />\n<br />\n先唔講係咪鬼<br />\n如果你係真心想表達意見，咁我都幾肯定你無響過去四個月汲取到經驗<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆不分化不篤灰 唔代表唔可以畀意見</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n套用幾個月年前成日玩膠嘅一句：<br />\n<strong>做法不完美，但可接受， 要改善</strong><br />\n見到咁個多怨氣post真係想作嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家係同一個團隊，就算你覺得兄弟有地方做錯，你提，OK，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但可唔可以唔好用一種「我啱你錯」嘅態度？</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋啲畀意見前<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">可唔可以唔好再做標題黨？</span></strong><br />\n一大堆「運動再唔XXX就一定輸」、放負屌柒人嘅標題<br />\n係呀啲人會click呀<br />\n但你覺得真係達到你嘅目的咩？<br />\n<br />\n講完，各位手足今日辛苦晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2591ac30330e910161f39bf269ce96b8e337845a","tid":1632061,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:54:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係外國既香港人都可以一齊係連登出力！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n4.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">外國巴打可以幫手文宣，尤其exchange學生，仲可以介紹俾其他國家既人</span></strong></span><br />\n5.擴大和理非平台，快速文宣，一個巴絲可翻譯，另一巴絲亦可做搬運工，快速輸出文宣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"d4069a63aff8933ef461e57024c50d397af4812f","tid":1632061,"uid":187812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:55:23.000Z","msg":"香港人俾政府恰到上心口！<br />\n「反蒙面法」繞過立法會直接立法，公然破壞香港法治制度。<br />\n三罷公投，投票表達意向！<br />\n<br />\n截至10月6日下午4點，我們收到超過32,000份有效回應。感謝大家支持，請繼續廣傳，全家總動員，一齊填問卷，我哋要更多，更多支持！<br />\n<br />\n請登入 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2nWkSyo&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEprP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=cf418cf2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo</a> 或掃QR code填寫問卷。<br />\n<br />\n公投截止日期：10月11日中午12點<br />\n<br />\nThe Government treat all HongKongers as nothing and they also passed the anti-mask law by Emergency Regulations Ordinance totally destroying judicial independence and the rule of law.<br />\nIt is time for us to speak up! Let&rsquo;s give your opinion on performing general strike.<br />\n<br />\nDeadline: 11 Oct 2019 1200 HKT<br />\nGoogle form link : <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2nWkSyo&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEprP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=cf418cf2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo</a>"},{"pid":"f24286a08d4cb5cd07a43a01e7be439681e64a6b","tid":1632061,"uid":219901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:55:41.000Z","msg":"唔推啦，有感而發，歡迎留意見"},{"pid":"08596e33b312ce2aa765a43e617ac3326b38a0d1","tid":1632061,"uid":202895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:56:42.000Z","msg":"通勝都為咗唔好輸輸聲，叫通勝啦<br />\n我地一定會贏架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc51f45592b2b6b92e91b247ccf85ad20a2b0ef8","tid":1632061,"uid":219901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08596e33b312ce2aa765a43e617ac3326b38a0d1","tid":1632061,"uid":202895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:56:42.000Z","msg":"通勝都為咗唔好輸輸聲，叫通勝啦<br />\n我地一定會贏架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:57:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fdfd862fc602f0cb8c6e0f9fed9f326aa88b5ca","tid":1632061,"uid":228458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:58:44.000Z","msg":"今日風向：勇武退場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631974\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631974</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"27532124aeb5a513cadf2c7a0a34309f0c032d13","tid":1632061,"uid":219901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:59:44.000Z","msg":"講漏左，如果明顯係分化post記得用不推文啦<br />\n目測得少過1/3人用<br />\n係咁幫人推post"},{"pid":"00ba574c2b593afdb60daf827186cd06dfdeda88","tid":1632061,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:00:04.000Z","msg":"俾意見從來唔係問題，問題係用詞語氣適宜溫和，不宜粗暴，等大家聽落舒服啲，自